  "detailed_description": "\"Colory Engine\" is the core component for all \"Colory\" Appslications.<br><br>Availabe DLCs are:<br>1. \"<strong>Colory VR Painter</strong>\": A virtual reality painting app<br>2. \"<strong>Colory STUDIO</strong>\": A desktop video editor for virtual production (currently beta user only).<br><br>The \"Colory\" Apps can be modded and extended by your own content with the free \"<strong>Colory Modkit</strong>\"<br><br>If you dont have any DLCs installed, \"Colory Engine\" will give you access to the free demo versions of the Colory apps.",
  "about_the_game": "\"Colory Engine\" is the core component for all \"Colory\" Appslications.<br><br>Availabe DLCs are:<br>1. \"<strong>Colory VR Painter</strong>\": A virtual reality painting app<br>2. \"<strong>Colory STUDIO</strong>\": A desktop video editor for virtual production (currently beta user only).<br><br>The \"Colory\" Apps can be modded and extended by your own content with the free \"<strong>Colory Modkit</strong>\"<br><br>If you dont have any DLCs installed, \"Colory Engine\" will give you access to the free demo versions of the Colory apps.",
